Lachlan ROTSCHREK, a/k/a Ciaran Templar-Obrien, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
13TH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT COURT, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3775 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 10, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The petition for writ of mandamus is dismissed as duplicative of the petition filed in case 2D18-3816. Petitioner's motion to expedite is denied as moot.

LaROSE, C.J., and MORRIS and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
